      "text": "5. Neim no winneem/ka tas\neffns tai Sa-eeschanas Telti par\nWaijadsibu/ un dohd teem Lewi-\nteem/ ikweenam pehz fawas Kal-\nposchanas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "6. Ta nehme Mohsus tahs\nKulbas / un tohs Wehrschus / un\ndewe tohs teem Lewiteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "7. Divi Rattus un tschetrus\nWehrschus dewe wiꞥsch Gersona\nDehleem/ pehz winnu Kalposcha-\nnas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Un tschetrus Rattus / un\nastox Wehrschus dewe wiꞥsch\nMerara Dehleem pehz winnu Kal-\nposchanas / appaffch Jhtamara\nRohkas / Airona ta Preestera\nDehla.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Bet Kaata Dehleem ne de-\nwe wiꞥsch neneeka / jo teem pee-\nnahze pee fwehtahn Leetahn\nkalpoht/ kas teem bija us faweein\nRaimefscheem janefs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Untec Wirsneeki uppureja\npar ta Altara Eefwehttischannu/tai\nDeenâ/ kad tas fwuidihts tappe/\ntad uppureja tee Wirsneeki fawus\nUppurus preekfch to Altari.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Un tas KUNGS fazzija\nus Mohsu: Akweenanu Wirsnee-\nkam buhs (iffwursch sawa Dee-\nnâ) fawus Uppurus / par Altara\nEefwehttischannu uppureht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12 Kas tad pirinâ Deenâ fa-\nru uppureja / tas btja\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Naëfons/ Amminadaba Dehle-\nno tahs Zilts Juha.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "13. Un winna Uppurs bi-\nweena fudraba Btohda /\nSwars bja fints un trihsdefinit\n(Sihkeli) weens fudraba Kan-\nno feptindefinits Sihketeem/pe-\ntahs fwehtas Weetas Sihkeli-\ntee abbee diwi bija pilni Kweefch-\nMiltu ar Etji fajauktu / par E-\ndamu-Uppuru.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "14. Weena selta Karrote n-\ndefinitis (Sihkeleem) pilna\nKwehpja-Sahlehun.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "15. Weens Wehrfens no le-\nleem Lohpeem / weens Auns-\nweens gadskahrtigs Jehrs/ pa-\nDedsann-Uppuri.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "16. Weens Ahsis par Grchku-\nUppuri.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Un par Pateiffschanas-Hi-\npuri diwi Wehrfchi / peez Aum-\npeez Ahschi / peez gadskahrtig-\nJehri / Schis bja tas Uppuri-\nNaëfona / Amminadaba Dehle-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Ohtrâ Deena uppurej-\nNetaneels / Zuara Dehls / Jhs-\nschara Wirfneeks.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "19. Wiꞥsch peeneffe par Satw-\nUppuri weenu fudrabaBtohdn/\nSwars bja fints un trihsde-\nmits Sihketi ; weenu fudrab-\nKansu no feptindefinits Sihk-\nteem / pehz tahs fwehtas Weeta-\nSihkeli / tee abbee diwi bija pil-\nKweefcho-Miltu ar Etji fajauktu-\npar Ehdamu-Uppuri.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
